room_title: Escape room "The List" by Expedition Escape in Montgomeryville
room_description: Uh oh! You've found out that you're on Santa's naughty list this year - and you know that this means there will not be any presents for you! Or does it? You've managed to find where the list is kept. The elves are on a break for the next 60 minutes. You have to find the list and escape before they come back!
